lead_paragraph: U.S. first lady Michelle Obama launched a 100-days from the Rio Olympics street party on Wednesday featuring more than 75 Olympians in an interactive carnival on two blocks of teeming Times Square.

headline.print_headline: Michelle Obama Keynotes 100-Days to Rio Games NYC Party
